channel.title: How to Hack Swords And Sandels Inc 9 Pics
channel.description:
Ok, This hack is for the online game... Swords And Sandals. The hack works for Both Swords and Sandals And Swords and Sandals 2.
Here is the link for the game = [url=http://www.swordsandsandals.com]http://www.swordsandsandals.com[/url]
Ok this is the way to hack it...
First you need Cheat engine....
Get From Here
[url=http://cheatengine.org/download.php]http://cheatengine.org/download.php[/url]
Install it and go on Swords and sandals... go on the screen where you choose your stats..
[b]Step 1)[/b] Then click on Cheat Engine And do this...
[IMG]http://i27.photobucket.com/albums/c163/i_kill_muhah/ss2.jpg[/img]
[b]Step 1B)[/b] When you have done that do this... (im using firefox so if you are.. click that)
[b]Step 2)[/b] Next... where is says Value... Put [b]8[/b] As shown below
[IMG]http://i27.photobucket.com/albums/c163/i_kill_muhah/ss3.jpg[/img]
[b]Step 3)[/b]Then click new scan A list should pop up after its finished like the one shown in the picture below....
[IMG]http://i27.photobucket.com/albums/c163/i_kill_muhah/ss4.jpg[/img]
[b]Step 4)[/b] Then go onto swords and sandals and change all the stats from 1 to 2 like in the picture below.
[IMG]http://i27.photobucket.com/albums/c163/i_kill_muhah/ss5.jpg[/img]
[b]Step 5)[/b] Then, where you put 8 before, put 16 and click Next Scan, This will Filter out all the ones that were prevously 8 that have now gone to 16... (Picture below)
[IMG]http://i27.photobucket.com/albums/c163/i_kill_muhah/ss6.jpg[/img]
Notice they have gone down to 12?
[IMG]http://i27.photobucket.com/albums/c163/i_kill_muhah/ss7.jpg[/img]
[b]Step 6)[/b] Now put the stats back to 1, and change the 16 back to 8, and click next scan again... you should come up with...
[IMG]http://i27.photobucket.com/albums/c163/i_kill_muhah/ss8.jpg[/img]
[b]Step 7)[/b] Now highlight them all and bring them down to where they are now...
[IMG]http://i27.photobucket.com/albums/c163/i_kill_muhah/ss9.jpg[/img]
[b]Step 8)[/b] Now click on one but double click it under the Value section... a box should pop up...
[IMG]http://i27.photobucket.com/albums/c163/i_kill_muhah/ss10.jpg[/img]
[b]Step 8)[/b] Change that 8 to any number that 8 goes into... if it isnt a multiple of 8 then it will crash..
For every 8 there is.. 1 stat will be added.. just do for all of the address's
For Example...
8 = 1 16 = 2 24 = 3 32 = 4 40 = 5 48 = 6 56 = 7 64 = 8 72 = 9 80 = 10
i would suggest not going over 160... it gets to stupid then...
Any Problems then message me on msn.... Thebeanie@gmail.com... Note: I Do NOT Discuss / Help With Private Servers Over Msn.. There is a PM system And a Development / Help for that.[br][size=1]Posted on: February 19, 2007, 03:50:20 AM[/size][hr]Pfft... 24 views no replys, i spent ages making this lmao
